headline: Jalapeño Hummus
name: Jalapeño Hummus
description: This jalapeño hummus is made by blending chickpeas, jalapeño peppers, garlic, cumin, and tahini to make a delicious dip that'll liven up any party!
recipeIngredient: 0.33333334326744 cup canned jalapeno pepper slices, juice reserved

recipeInstructions.text: Place chickpeas, jalapeño peppers and reserved juice, tahini, garlic, and lemon juice in a blender or food processor; season with cumin, curry powder, and crushed red pepper. Blend until smooth.
